              {
                "lang_tag": "ui7_kitdevice_6221_step_4_01",
                "text": "For best results pairing should be done within 10 feet (3 meters) of your Vera.<br>\nPress the Action Button twice within 1 second on your WallMote. The LED will start flashing Blue for a few seconds, turn solid Blue for 2 seconds, and then turn off indicating pairing is successful."
              }
            ]
