                "lang_tag": "ui7_kitdevice_6221_step_4_11",
                "text": "If the device isn't detected within 60 seconds or the LED turns Red for 2 seconds and then turns off, click the 'Retry' button below to begin un-pairing the device."
              }
            ]
          }
